{"tid":626953,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鄭松泰快被剝奪政治權利　最快5月9日被僭奪議員資格","createTime":"2018-04-12T14:14:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-14T13:49:20.000Z","uid":47714,"like":54,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"599893454307ecad197936c0127b86f2e0ea61b5","tid":626953,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T14:14:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180412/20359168\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180412%2F20359168&d=barE%2FgOtKSgBVCbrlwDp0SwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=76835e07\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180412%2F20359168&h=406aa6be\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180412/20359168</a><br />\n<br />\n立法會調查熱血公民鄭松泰倒插國旗事件委員會提交報告，裁定鄭行為違反誓言及行為不檢，足以構成譴責理據。委員會主席梁美芬稱，鄭一再作出侮辱國旗和國家的行為，令市民反感，已非一般的行為不檢，又建議立會於5月9日的大會就譴責議案辯論和表決，一但通過鄭就會被褫奪議員資格。鄭松泰反駁建制派欲加之罪，質疑委員會根本早有結論，有民主派表明會反對譴責議案。"},{"pid":"527c0ba5fcf49b9ffa3937113fedccd8a379c014","tid":626953,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T06:36:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f26d1596ef6903e588c0d700f868eb56fa610ebf","tid":626953,"uid":33481,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T06:38:27.000Z","msg":"快<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9fd59da538ef13cffef9f6a56871b8540c132d2","tid":626953,"uid":47359,"like":10,"dislike":3,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T06:40:29.000Z","msg":"泛民心諗又有機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c99c1d20d44d00999a6b3efb903886f1e054e840",